column2: SELECT    s.specObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.class, s.zWarning, s.snMedian, bcg.ra_bcg, bcg.dec_bcg, mass.* into mydb.bcg2#_stellarMassStarformingPort from mydb.bcg2#_radec as bcg      CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjEq(bcg.ra_bcg,bcg.dec_bcg, #) AS near      JOIN SpecObjAll as s ON near.specObjID=s.specObjID     JOIN stellarMassStarformingPort AS mass ON mass.specObjID = near.specObjID
